<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>CartoonCraze</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: system-ui;
      background: #f06d06;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    header.hero {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    section {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .art-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .art-grid img {
      max-width: 200px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    input, textarea {
      padding: 0.5rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    button {
      background: white;
      color: #f06d06;
      padding: 0.7rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 1rem;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="hero">
    <h1>CartoonCraze</h1>
    <p>imaginative cartoon art</p>
  </header>

  <section class="about">
    <h2>About the Artist</h2>
    <p>Welcome to CartoonCraze! I'm B.O.B, a cartoon artist who brings characters to life with a splash of color and a lot of attitude. From whimsical creatures to zany expressions, my work is all about fun and storytelling through art.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="gallery">
    <h2>Gallery</h2>
    <div class="art-grid">
      <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/e/e5/FinnAdventureTime.png" alt="Finn from Adventure Time">
      <!-- Add more images as needed -->
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact">
    <h2>Contact Me</h2>
    <form action="mailto:youremail@example.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain">
      <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
      <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
      <textarea name="message" placeholder="Tell me what you think!" required></textarea>
      <button type="submit">Send</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 CartoonCraze. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementsByTagName("h1")[0].style.fontSize = "6vw";
  </script>

</body>
</html>
